-- Mazor Rises Most in a Month After Loss Narrows as Revenue Climbs
-- B y   S h o s h a n n a   S o l o m o n
-- 2012-05-16T09:45:54Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-16/mazor-rises-most-in-a-month-after-loss-narrows-as-revenue-climbs.html
  Mazor Robotics Ltd. (MZOR)  gained the most
in more than a month after the developer of surgical robots said
its first-quarter loss narrowed as revenue rose 45 percent.  The  shares  advanced 4.9 percent, the most since April 11,
to 4.25 shekels at 12:30 p.m. in  Tel Aviv .  The net loss narrowed to 4.7 million shekels ($1.2 million)
from 5.6 million shekels in the year-earlier period. Revenue
surged to 9.2 million shekels.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Shoshanna Solomon in Tel Aviv at 
 ssolomon22@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
